Andy Warhol Died in 1987 When he was Only 58 after Complications

00:05:34.380 --> 00:05:37.399
Following Routine Gallbladder Surgery in A new York Hospital

00:05:37.919 --> 00:05:42.589
He is buried at a small Cemetery near Where he was Born in Bethel Park Pennsylvania

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:50.529
